DRBD Management Console
by Rasto Levrinc

to compile and run type: ant

you may need to provide following jars in build-lib/ directory in order to
build it:
jai_core.jar junit.jar

for sudo you would need at least this commands in the sudoers file:

rasto ALL=SETENV: /usr/local/bin/drbd-gui-helper-*, /sbin/drbdadm,
/usr/sbin/cibadmin, /usr/sbin/crm_resource, /usr/sbin/crm_attribute,
/usr/sbin/ptest

